simple_athena_query: SELECT * FROM planet WHERE type = 'node' AND tags['amenity'] IN ('hospital', 'clinic', 'doctors') limit 10
bigquery_script: DECLARE var_Example INT64 DEFAULT 1; select ST_GEOGPOINT(-72, 51) as GeoPoint
simple_snowflake_query: SELECT ROUND(uniform(-90::float, 90::float, random()), 6) AS lat, ROUND(uniform(-180::float, 180::float, random()), 6) AS lon FROM TABLE(GENERATOR(ROWCOUNT => 100))
